spec_data.Name: texlive-pagecont
spec_data.Description:
The package provides the facility that several documents can be
typeset independently with page numbers in sequence, as if they
were a single document.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:11:54 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Page numbering that continues between documents
